### Generate Invoice
POST http://localhost:4000/v1/documents/generate
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_JWT>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "commerce/invoice",
  "record_id": "<UUID_OF_AN_ORDER>"
}

### Generate Brochure
POST http://localhost:4000/v1/documents/generate
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_JWT>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "marketing/brochure",
  "record_id": "<UUID_OF_A_PRODUCT>"
}